reviewText: Part was good, half was poor quality!!!
The cd's that I received were corrupted and I could only see portions of the videos.  What I did see were funny. I am sending it back and am asking for a replacement.  Hopefully, they will be better.
The Stoop focused mainly with The Bronx  I had a stoop in Manhattan.  It delivered some memories but not from my block.
I ordered a DVD on December 12 and as of January 16, I still have not received it. After reviewing the feedback, this seems to be a common problem.
